1
00:00:36,840 --> 00:00:38,679
What kind of person is this Wang Yingrong?

2
00:00:38,759 --> 00:00:39,640
She is simply shameless.

3
00:00:39,799 --> 00:00:40,840
In front of so many people...

4
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:41,759
...saying she likes you.

5
00:00:41,880 --> 00:00:43,759
What decent family's daughter acts like that?

6
00:00:44,079 --> 00:00:45,399
Look at the trouble you've caused.

7
00:00:45,640 --> 00:00:47,159
A young girl...

8
00:00:47,320 --> 00:00:48,840
...publicly saying she likes an enemy.

9
00:00:49,200 --> 00:00:50,560
And she even got rejected.

10
00:00:50,799 --> 00:00:53,079
How will the Wang family ever show their faces?

11
00:00:53,280 --> 00:00:53,920
Mom.

12
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:55,600
Can't you see it?

13
00:00:56,359 --> 00:00:58,039
Yingrong was trying to help me today.

14
00:00:58,280 --> 00:01:00,560
She wanted to draw this curse onto herself.

15
00:01:01,079 --> 00:01:02,320
And clear my name completely.

16
00:01:03,479 --> 00:01:04,280
It was me...

17
00:01:05,439 --> 00:01:06,799
...who didn't think as far ahead as she did.

18
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:08,599
I didn't protect her well enough.

19
00:01:09,079 --> 00:01:10,879
Look at the things you've done lately.

20
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:13,400
Is there a single thing people haven't criticized?

21
00:01:13,879 --> 00:01:16,359
Director Zhang's wife came to our door to curse you.

22
00:01:16,879 --> 00:01:18,439
Raising pigs angered the public.

23
00:01:18,599 --> 00:01:19,840
And recklessly...

24
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:21,000
...opening some Vinegar Workshop.

25
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:22,640
And now, with that...

26
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:24,599
...Zheng Minjiang, who's had a wife...

27
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:25,920
...you're entangled in a mess.

28
00:01:26,159 --> 00:01:27,000
Everyone's spit alone...

29
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:29,120
...is enough to drown our whole family.

30
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:31,200
Sister Yingrong was just so cool.

31
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:32,439
She is my role model.

32
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:33,359
Brother.

33
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:34,640
You compared to her...

34
00:01:34,959 --> 00:01:36,439
...are miles apart.

35
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:37,359
Such a big bowl...

36
00:01:37,439 --> 00:01:38,200
...can't stop your mouth?

37
00:01:38,359 --> 00:01:38,879
Eat.

38
00:01:40,079 --> 00:01:42,359
There was nothing wrong with what I did.

39
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,879
You are just unrepentant.

40
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:47,200
I gave birth to three daughters...

41
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,439
...so I'm already a cut below others.

42
00:01:48,599 --> 00:01:49,959
And you just have to be a disappointment.

43
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:52,319
Mom.

44
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:54,680
I don't think girls are worse than boys.

45
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:56,400
They have their good lives.

46
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:57,439
And we have ours.

47
00:01:59,319 --> 00:02:01,719
You still think everything you did was right.

48
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:02,719
She helped you?

49
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,959
I think she has designs on you.

50
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:06,359
You were right to reject her today.

51
00:02:06,519 --> 00:02:08,280
I think she just wanted to climb the ladder.

52
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,879
Our Zheng family must never let that Wang family...

53
00:02:09,879 --> 00:02:10,919
...splash dirty water on us.

54
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:12,319
We should stay as far away as possible.

55
00:02:12,639 --> 00:02:13,439
Getting involved with that Wang family...

56
00:02:13,439 --> 00:02:14,639
...means being cursed for generations.

57
00:02:14,759 --> 00:02:15,840
Nothing good comes of it.

58
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,719
Zheng Haiyang, Zheng Xiaochuan.

59
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:18,919
You two listen up.

60
00:02:19,199 --> 00:02:20,199
Watch your big brother.

61
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:20,879
Whatever Big Brother does...

62
00:02:20,879 --> 00:02:21,719
...you do the same.

63
00:02:22,039 --> 00:02:22,719
The three of you...

64
00:02:22,919 --> 00:02:24,599
...must have your own principles and stance.

65
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:26,039
Don't let that homewrecker from the Wang family...

66
00:02:26,039 --> 00:02:27,080
...seduce you all.

67
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:27,800
Mom.

68
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:29,919
In the future, don't...

69
00:02:29,919 --> 00:02:31,280
...keep calling Yingrong a homewrecker.

70
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,639
You're talking back to me?

71
00:02:34,039 --> 00:02:34,919
Fine then.

72
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:37,400
If you're so capable, cut ties with our family.

73
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:38,879
Get out!

74
00:02:39,199 --> 00:02:40,360
Go as far away as possible!

75
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:41,840
Whatever you want to do...

76
00:02:42,039 --> 00:02:43,120
...is none of our business.

77
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,599
Just don't drag our whole family down.

78
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,759
Since I've embarrassed you...

79
00:02:50,439 --> 00:02:51,039
I'll leave.

80
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:55,280
Yingrong.

81
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:57,560
Let her go.

82
00:02:58,039 --> 00:02:59,159
I see your wings have hardened.

83
00:03:06,759 --> 00:03:08,400
What are you looking at? Eat.

84
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,080
Brother

85
00:03:59,759 --> 00:04:01,800
Why did you reject Wang Yingrong today?

86
00:04:02,639 --> 00:04:03,680
Do you not like her,

87
00:04:04,039 --> 00:04:05,639
or was it to distance yourself to protect her?

88
00:04:10,599 --> 00:04:11,479
I do like her,

89
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,000
but I also want to protect her.

90
00:04:15,479 --> 00:04:16,560
Especially when her mom

91
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:18,279
and those people don't believe her.

92
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,519
Then do you know she likes you?

93
00:04:22,879 --> 00:04:24,879
How could she really like me?

94
00:04:26,639 --> 00:04:27,920
Given the situation today,

95
00:04:29,079 --> 00:04:30,480
she used that method to help us out.

96
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,480
She's really smart.

97
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,040
Do you really think

98
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,600
she did it just to help out?

99
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,040
What else?

100
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,160
How could she possibly like

101
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,519
a man who's been married?

102
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,319
She said those things

103
00:04:46,639 --> 00:04:48,240
just because she didn't want to put me in a tough spot.

104
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:52,040
How could I let her get dragged into this mess?

105
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:54,439
Have you ever thought

106
00:04:54,439 --> 00:04:56,040
that sometimes, once you miss a chance, it's gone?

107
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:58,000
It's true for beautiful things,

108
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:59,199
and it's true for people too.

109
00:05:16,959 --> 00:05:18,199
You're sleeping here alone?

110
00:05:18,199 --> 00:05:19,720
Why didn't you even close the door?

111
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:20,560
Sis.

112
00:05:21,199 --> 00:05:22,199
Why are you here?

113
00:05:23,199 --> 00:05:24,720
If I didn't bring you bedding,

114
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:27,000
were you really planning to sleep just like this?

115
00:05:30,839 --> 00:05:32,040
How can you sleep here?

116
00:05:32,319 --> 00:05:33,839
Why don't you go back home to sleep?

117
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,959
There's no place for me at home anymore.

118
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,000
Actually,

119
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:47,079
today,

120
00:05:47,879 --> 00:05:50,079
I really admired you.

121
00:05:54,319 --> 00:05:56,199
Sis, you don't need to comfort me.

122
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:57,600
I...

123
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:00,120
I just did it to help him.

124
00:06:02,319 --> 00:06:03,800
I'm not comforting you.

125
00:06:03,959 --> 00:06:05,240
I'm telling the truth.

126
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:08,560
My little sister is so good,

127
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,319
it's Zheng Minjiang who isn't good enough.

128
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:16,040
Sis.

129
00:06:16,439 --> 00:06:17,399
I'm fine.

130
00:06:17,879 --> 00:06:19,000
I've said what I said.

131
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,560
Whether he accepts it is his business.

132
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:23,480
I just want to run the Vinegar Workshop well now.

133
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:25,639
To provide security for you and Bao'er.

134
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,720
But the most important thing is,

135
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:29,920
I want you to

136
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:32,079
live a good life.

137
00:06:32,639 --> 00:06:35,199
You living well is what matters most.

138
00:06:35,439 --> 00:06:36,079
You know?

139
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:40,720
Come here.

140
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,040
Let me help you make the bed.

141
00:06:54,639 --> 00:06:55,439
Yingrong

142
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:56,360
Uncle Fang

143
00:06:57,319 --> 00:06:59,480
Thanks for helping me load this batch of grain.

144
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,040
Well, that's just because...

145
00:07:01,199 --> 00:07:02,920
I'm looking forward to your Baliang Vinegar.

146
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,360
It's all good now.

147
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,879
Once this grain is in the warehouse,

148
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,600
later on, I can just wait in the shop

149
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:09,639
for the new vinegar you brew.

150
00:07:09,759 --> 00:07:10,199
Okay.

151
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,839
When it's brewed, I'll send it over to you.

152
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:12,879
I'll be waiting then.

153
00:07:13,319 --> 00:07:13,720
Alright.

154
00:07:14,319 --> 00:07:15,279
I have other things to do.

155
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:16,240
I'll get going now.

156
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:16,920
I'll let you get back to work.

157
00:07:16,959 --> 00:07:17,319
Okay.

158
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,279
Thanks, Uncle Fang.

159
00:07:18,399 --> 00:07:19,160
You're welcome.

160
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,279
Take it easy moving it.

161
00:07:22,279 --> 00:07:22,959
Will do.

162
00:07:22,959 --> 00:07:23,639
Open it and take a look.

163
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:31,720
How is it?

164
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:32,720
It's pretty good.

165
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:34,040
My second aunt said,

166
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,240
brewing vinegar requires good grain,

167
00:07:35,319 --> 00:07:36,560
sweet water, and clean vessels.

168
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:37,959
Come on, unload the truck.

169
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:39,839
You...

170
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:49,360
Actually, would you consider me?

171
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,160
Second Brother.

172
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:52,000
Second Brother.

173
00:07:52,199 --> 00:07:52,720
Second Brother.

174
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:56,040
Second Brother.

175
00:07:56,319 --> 00:07:57,519
Mom's calling you home for dinner.

176
00:07:58,399 --> 00:07:59,560
I need to keep watch here tonight.

177
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:01,800
Find an excuse to cover for me.

178
00:08:03,319 --> 00:08:04,639
How did this become my problem?

179
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:06,079
It's no big deal.

180
00:08:06,199 --> 00:08:06,920
You go back first.

181
00:08:07,399 --> 00:08:08,879
Actually, I'm not afraid of Mom knowing.

182
00:08:09,759 --> 00:08:10,720
There's no need to hide it either.

183
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,199
Easy for you to say.

184
00:08:12,279 --> 00:08:13,680
Don't you know what Mom's temper is like?

185
00:08:15,439 --> 00:08:17,480
The whole thing with Sister Yingrong confessing to Big Brother...

186
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:19,399
Mom still hasn't gotten over it.

187
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,839
And now you're stirring up trouble again.

188
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:22,879
You guys are ganging up on me.

189
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:35,720
Why is it getting dark so fast?

190
00:08:37,399 --> 00:08:39,200
Why isn't there a single soul here?

191
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,320
You... you...

192
00:08:59,399 --> 00:09:00,279
What do you want?

193
00:09:00,919 --> 00:09:01,759
You're so careless when you walk.

194
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:03,720
Here.

195
00:09:16,639 --> 00:09:17,600
Sorry.

196
00:09:18,039 --> 00:09:19,960
I thought you were a bad guy just now.

197
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:29,200
Can you still walk?

198
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:31,559
I can.

199
00:09:48,159 --> 00:09:49,279
Thanks for earlier.

200
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:57,399
Actually, you don't need to walk me home.

201
00:09:58,840 --> 00:09:59,639
It's on my way.

202
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:04,440
Do you know me?

203
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:06,639
Otherwise, how would I know

204
00:10:07,919 --> 00:10:08,759
it's on the way?

205
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:10,840
There's only one road here.

206
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,159
I'm here.

207
00:10:46,679 --> 00:10:47,720
I'm here too.

208
00:10:52,679 --> 00:10:53,600
Fang Fang.

209
00:10:54,919 --> 00:10:56,720
Why did you come over so late?

210
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,600
It's my dad.

211
00:10:58,600 --> 00:11:00,240
He told me to come learn from you.

212
00:11:00,759 --> 00:11:02,000
Nonsense.

213
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,600
What is there to learn this late?

214
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:07,000
Did you sneak out on your own?

215
00:11:08,399 --> 00:11:09,360
Sister Yingrong.

216
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:11,240
My dad rushes me to get married every day.

217
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:12,679
My ears are growing calluses.

218
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,679
But I heard...

219
00:11:14,759 --> 00:11:16,399
...there's a long line of people chasing you.

220
00:11:16,879 --> 00:11:17,519
What's wrong?

221
00:11:17,679 --> 00:11:18,639
Don't you like any of them?

222
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,440
Those people...

223
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,919
...swarm around me like flies.

224
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:24,559
They're just after my dad's money.

225
00:11:24,679 --> 00:11:25,759
It's so annoying.

226
00:11:27,399 --> 00:11:28,000
Sister Yingrong.

227
00:11:28,399 --> 00:11:29,080
Let me tell you.

228
00:11:29,559 --> 00:11:31,840
I met a man on the way here just now.

229
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:33,080
He escorted me the whole way.

230
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:35,879
Do you think he likes me?

231
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:37,559
Do you know him?

232
00:11:38,159 --> 00:11:39,360
We just met.

233
00:11:39,799 --> 00:11:40,879
He followed behind me...

234
00:11:40,879 --> 00:11:41,919
...and even gave me a flashlight.

235
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:43,120
He escorted me all the way.

236
00:11:45,399 --> 00:11:47,200
He must have fallen in love at first sight.

237
00:11:47,879 --> 00:11:49,919
He wants to pursue me but is too shy.

238
00:11:50,639 --> 00:11:52,159
He insisted it was just on his way.

239
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,480
I cleared the stones at the entrance.

240
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:55,879
Good.

241
00:11:58,480 --> 00:11:59,000
You...

242
00:11:59,399 --> 00:11:59,919
You...

243
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:01,799
You're from the Vinegar Workshop.

244
00:12:03,039 --> 00:12:04,279
Yes, my neighbor.

245
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:05,000
Zheng Haiyang.

246
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:14,200
So it really was on the way.

247
00:12:14,879 --> 00:12:15,759
Do you know each other?

248
00:12:16,039 --> 00:12:16,840
We do. No, we don't.

249
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,240
I mistook him for someone else.

250
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:22,480
I don't know him.

251
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:26,480
Don't break my flashlight.

252
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:27,000
It's quite expensive.

253
00:12:29,919 --> 00:12:31,519
You give it to someone, then take it back?

254
00:12:39,399 --> 00:12:40,000
Haiyang.

255
00:12:41,879 --> 00:12:42,360
This is...

256
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:44,080
...Uncle Fang's daughter, Fang Fang.

257
00:12:46,679 --> 00:12:47,480
It's so late.

258
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:48,879
Walk her home in a bit.

259
00:12:50,879 --> 00:12:51,399
Sure thing.

260
00:12:58,360 --> 00:12:58,919
Let's go.

261
00:13:02,879 --> 00:13:03,720
I'm going to walk her home then.

262
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:25,480
Stand properly.

263
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:27,559
Director Zhen.

264
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:30,240
We've been looking forward to your arrival.

265
00:13:31,759 --> 00:13:32,360
Xiao Wu.

266
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:33,519
Director Zhen.

267
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:36,159
Xiao Wu.

268
00:13:39,639 --> 00:13:40,320
Li Guangming.

269
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:41,600
Li Guangming from the production workshop.

270
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,200
Where is Minjiang?

271
00:13:47,919 --> 00:13:48,759
Minjiang...

272
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:50,919
He said he has something to do and can't make it.

273
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:55,120
Minjiang.

274
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:05,919
Teacher Zhen.

275
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:07,240
Why are you here?

276
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:08,200
Minjiang.

277
00:14:08,519 --> 00:14:09,320
What are you talking about?

278
00:14:09,639 --> 00:14:10,600
Who is your teacher?

279
00:14:10,879 --> 00:14:12,080
Go pour tea for Director Zhen, quick.
